query:
INSERT INTO exercises (
    id,
    exam_id,
    name,
    deadline,
    page_id,
    score_maximum,
    order_number,
    chapter_id,
    copied_from,
    max_tries_per_slide,
    limit_number_of_tries,
    needs_peer_review,
    use_course_default_peer_or_self_review_config,
    needs_self_review,
    teacher_reviews_answer_after_locking
  )
SELECT uuid_generate_v5($1, id::text),
  $1,
  name,
  deadline,
  uuid_generate_v5($1, page_id::text),
  score_maximum,
  order_number,
  NULL,
  id,
  max_tries_per_slide,
  limit_number_of_tries,
  needs_peer_review,
  use_course_default_peer_or_self_review_config,
  needs_self_review,
  teacher_reviews_answer_after_locking
FROM exercises
WHERE exam_id = $2
  AND deleted_at IS NULL
RETURNING id,
  copied_from;
